<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Password Reset OTP</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
            color: #333;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: auto;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .otp {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #007BFF;
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <p>Your OTP for password reset is:</p>
        <p class="otp">{{otp}}</p>
        <p>This OTP is valid for 15 minutes.</p>
        <div class="footer">
            If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
